post_install(){
 cat <<INFO

To load the OWASP ModSecurity Core Rule Set in NginX,
add the following directives to your NginX configuration:

    load_module "/usr/lib/nginx/modules/ngx_http_modsecurity_module.so";
    http {
        modsecurity on;
        modsecurity_rules_file /etc/modsecurity/load.conf;
        modsecurity_transaction_id "$request_id";
    }

INFO
}
